longBusinessSummary: Dignitana AB (publ.), a medical technology company, develops, produces, and markets medical cooling devices primarily in the United States. It offers DigniCap, a scalp cooling system used to reduce hair loss from certain chemotherapy treatments, as well as in the treatment of breast cancer. Dignitana AB (publ.) was incorporated in 2007 is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
